      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ISLE OF LACHLAN (3) has been impressive at his past couple of wins, the best coming last time at this track in 25.47. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. The hardest to beat again. RINA DUTTON (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 25.55 beating HOLLY'S BEAR. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Deserves serious consideration again. BING BONUS (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (25.90) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Hard to beat again. HOLLY'S BEAR (7) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
